name: A Pocketful of Stars
description:
Many colourful stars are packed close together in this image of the globular cluster NGC 1805, taken by the NASA/ESA Hubble Space Telescope. 

Name:	NGC 1805
Type:	Milky Way : Star : Grouping : Cluster : Globular
Constellation:	Dorado
Category:	Star Clusters
